      "alignment": "NE",
      "biography": {
        "value": "\n                        Forged in the crucible of countless battles, this goblin rose through the ranks through sheer brutality and cunning. It commands a fearsome warband, leaving a trail of destruction in its wake.\n                        <hr>\n                        <p><strong>Behavior:</strong> This goblin is a brutal leader, inspiring fear and loyalty in equal measure. It commands its minions with harsh words and a terrifying presence, always seeking to crush its enemies with overwhelming force.</p>\n                        <p><strong>Appearance:</strong> A hulking goblin, larger and more scarred than its kin, clad in gleaming plate armor. Its eyes burn with a malevolent intelligence, and it wields a scimitar wreathed in flames.</p>\n                        <p><strong>Twist:</strong> Despite its cruelty, the Warlord harbors a secret fear of true magic, often targeting spellcasters first.</p>\n                        <p><strong>Habitat:</strong> Dark caves, ruined fortresses, or anywhere it can establish a brutal domain.</p>\n                        <p><strong>Treasure:</strong> The Flaming Scimitar, 200 gp, assorted gems worth 500 gp.</p>\n                    "
      },
